PROCEDURE speckle(screen2%)
  LOCAL xa&
  DIM xb&(31999)
  HIDEM
  FOR xa&=0 TO 31999
    xb&(xa&)=xa&
  NEXT xa&
  FOR xa&=0 TO 31999
    SWAP xb&(xa&),xb&(RANDOM(32000))
  NEXT xa&
  FOR xa&=0 TO 31999
    POKE XBIOS(2)+xb&(xa&),PEEK(screen2%+xb&(xa&))
  NEXT xa&
  ERASE xb&()
  SHOWM
RETURN
